Using in Maven

  The library is available as a Maven module.  Simply add the following dependencies:

+---+
<dependencies>
    <dependency>
        <groupId>org.onebusaway</groupId>
        <artifactId>onebusaway-siri-core</artifactId>
        <version>${currentVersion}</version>
    </dependency>
</dependencies>
+---+